rstood.\n\nApp completely offline. No require internet to study\nSearch by French or English\nSave your favorite sentences for review later\nWhen you travel, business to France, don t forget this app\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'https://apkpure.com/learn-french-offline/com.ufo.learnfrance/download?from=home', '1.5', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/mntV09IuIwrVrRmI6xvMt1RYSm67BsUYVy5o8gez0jEWinbbwMzuFIutMu6mpH6zKtw=w72', 0, 4, 1141, 50, '2017-01-30 06:52:09', 'com.ufo.learnfrance', 0),
