he pretty pictures \n?Overview Mode: Quickly overview all the cards \n?Shuffle Mode: Help to memorize and examine your learning\n\n--- Learn from 12 Languages Translated by Native Speakers ---\nEnglish, French, Spanish, Japanese, Korean, Simplified Chinese (Mandarin), Traditional Chinese, Cantonese, Portuguese, Turkish, Dutch, Polish\n\nOur international team loves promoting foreign languages and diverse cultures. We have 10-year experiences in teaching languages to foreigners and kids in the real life. \n\nThis app is adopting our teaching experience plus scientific methods to raise your interests and enable you to learn effectively.\nVoice from native speaker, accurate grammar.\n\n--- FREE Contents --- \nPlay cards, get experience points, level up and collect new cards for free! \nLet s learn like playing games!\n\nMore than 30 categories include: \n?Basic Conversations, Greetings \n?Numbers, Colors, Animals \n?Restaurant, Food, Vegetables, Fruits\n?Sightseeing, Transportation, Shopping, Hotel (newly added)\n?Body, Date, Family, Directions, Weather (newly added)\n?Occupations, Hobbies and more (coming soon)\n\nAre you planning to travel Berlin or other region in Germany?\nDo you want to learn some basic phrases, words and enjoy the conversation during the trip?\nLet s start it now!\n\n\nFeedback: support.googleplay@lingo-apps.com\nFacebook: http://www.facebook.com/LingoCards\nWeb: http://www.lingo-apps.com\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n', 'https://apkpure.com/learn&read-german-travel-words/kuma.lingocards.german/download?from=home', '1.5', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/DYY3c2FyUZKBqFuN5dbxTJWL6rxZHe-wZHKbIpj2FIv0QGkTaucD9YFZ9NFmsfZDxyQ=w72', 0, 4, 60, 5, '2017-01-30 07:00:00', 'kuma.lingocards.german', 0);
