l.\n\n------------------------------\n\nHere s what you ll love about Outlook for Android:\n\n• Seamless inbox management with a focused inbox that displays your most important messages first, swipe gestures and smart filters. \n\n• Easy access to calendar and files right from your inbox. \n\n• Features to work on the go, like Word, Excel and PowerPoint integrations.', 'https://apkpure.com/microsoft-outlook/com.microsoft.office.outlook/download?from=home', '2.1.138', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/_gpQ5T1jLbbpyoaDHgYoJV_seHudPYAqfYe7me5MApKMYUuY91E_h6y3Jy_Cxe8OO8E=w72', 0, 4, 1227806, 50, '2017-02-04 11:24:44', 'com.microsoft.office.outlook', 0);
