iling app, or the SeableApps site when you click a button.\r\nAccess Storage - Used to save and retrieve app settings on your phone.', 'http://touchitappstore.com/it_api/apk/Dice.apk', 'v4.1', 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/3V_NEwtAHZjlsjCKY0qiuDBvw1HhTSglLmp2wd2ptw0ChPDeZ05T8QT7MSTulFcd3-Yc=w72', 0, 5, 496, 100, '2017-03-18 06:18:12', 'appinventor.ai_ansonsavage.DiceRole_Magic8Ball_Extension_Two_Die', 1),
